'''本特利'''（{{lang-en|Bentley}}）是[[英格蘭|英格蘭]][[漢普郡|漢普郡]][[東漢普區|東漢普區]]的村莊與[[民政教區|民政教區]]。該教區面積為{{convert|2299|acre|km2}}。該村莊剛好位於連接[[薩里郡|薩里郡]][[法納姆|法納姆]]與[[奧爾頓_(漢普郡)|奧爾頓]]之間的[[A31公路|A31公路]]，距法納姆西方約8公里（5英里）遠，距奧爾頓東方約10公里（6英里）。該地的[[本特利火車站_(漢普郡)|火車站]]距離南方的[[賓斯特德|賓斯特德]]民政教區約1.6公里（1英里）<ref>{{cite web|title=GB Historical GIS / University of Portsmouth, History of Bentley in East Hampshire|url=http://www.visionofbritain.org.uk/place/4678|publisher=Map and description, A Vision of Britain through Time|accessdate=2013-12-09|archive-date=2020-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201024202405/https://www.visionofbritain.org.uk/place/4678|dead-url=no}}</ref>。 

該村莊有2個客棧：The Star<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://thestarinnbentley.co.uk/default.aspx |title=The Star Inn, Bentley |access-date=2013-12-09 |archive-date=2012-01-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120113042233/http://thestarinnbentley.co.uk/default.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>與The Bull<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.beerintheevening.com/pubs/s/32/32729/Bull_Inn/Bentley |title=The Bull Inn, Bentley |access-date=2013-12-09 |archive-date=2020-11-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201126150756/http://beerintheevening.com/pubs/s/32/32729/Bull_Inn/Bentley |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

